{{unreferenced|date=February 2014}}
{{TOC_right}} [[United Medical and Dental College|In]] [[Pakistan]], a [[medical school]] is more often referred to as a medical college. A medical college is affiliated with a university as a department which usually has a separate campus. The medical schools in province of [[Sindh]] are both private and public.
