{{distinguish|Initiative for Open Citations}}
'''OpenCitations''' (established in 2010{{citation needed|date=March 2018}}) is a project aiming to publish [[open access|open]] bibliographic [[citation]] information in [[Resource Description Framework|RDF]]. It produces the "OpenCitations Corpus" database.<ref>{{citation |url=https://opencitations.wordpress.com/2018/01/29/opencitations-and-the-initiative-for-open-citations-a-clarification/ |title=OpenCitations and the Initiative for Open Citations: A Clarification |author=David Shotton |date=January 29, 2018 }}</ref>

